00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,767
Add Audio to Hotspot

2
00:00:00,767 --> 00:00:03,103
First, go to the main menu and click “Media Library”

3
00:00:03,103 --> 00:00:05,372
Click “Audio files”

4
00:00:05,372 --> 00:00:10,377
Add a audio file from computer to library

5
00:00:10,377 --> 00:00:13,046
Now return to CTA menu, and create a CTA area

6
00:00:13,046 --> 00:00:14,948
Click “Play Audio” on the left menu

7
00:00:14,948 --> 00:00:20,687
Select “Add from Media Library” from right menu

8
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:27,394
Add the audio file you just added

9
00:00:27,394 --> 00:00:31,631
OK, let’s preview

10
00:00:31,631 --> 00:00:39,806
Click the hotspot area, the audio file will play
